text.tspan: Production vs. consumption-based CO₂ emissions per capita, United
Consumption-based emissions are national emissions that have been adjusted for trade. It's production-based emissions minus
emissions embedded in exports, plus emissions embedded in imports.
Source: Our World in Data based on the Global Carbon Project (2022)
